data.description: Welcome to this beautiful, open concept home in Telfair where the vaulted ceilings and natural light will have your heart! Recent improvements include new roof (Nov 2022), new HVAC (Aug 2020), new hot water heater (2019), and new carpet in downstairs bedrooms (Jan 2023). Living room features a wood burning fireplace and french doors that lead onto the spacious sunroom. Enjoy the 4th bedroom or bonus room above the garage. The huge backyard is completely fenced in for additional privacy. This is a great home in a quiet neighborhood close to Parris Island, MCAS, Historic Downtown Beaufort, schools, shopping, restaurants, and more. Best of all enjoy no HOAs!
